Class AnEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.reading.syrvanser.Entities.AnEntity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Food, LifeForm, Obstacle

    public abstract class AnEntity
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class representing a simple Entity Stores information about name, position, energy, etc. All entities inherit from this class

    10/10/2016.
